{"parentUuid":"62e950a7-bab6-4eba-9295-556418ccabd8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CcxxXMH4HSpswd4NCrBar","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The signup form is on the canvas and validated on the first push — no spec issues came back.\n\nHow it's put together:\n\n- **State** is seeded as `form: { name: \"\", email: \"\", password: \"\" }`, so all three inputs are controlled from the start rather than flipping from uncontrolled to controlled on first keystroke.\n- **Each Input** binds its `value` with `$bindState` to its slot under `form`, which gives two-way binding: typing writes straight back into state.\n- **Name** is a required text input, **email** is `type: \"email\"` and required, and **password** is `type: \"password\"`, required, with `minLength: 8` plus a description line telling the user about the 8-character floor.\n- **The \"Sign up\" button** fires `canvas.submit` on click, with the whole `form` object passed as the payload via `$state`, so the submit handler receives the name, email, and password together."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1155,"cache_read_input_tokens":4415,"output_tokens":280,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1155,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":280,"cache_read_input_tokens":4415,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1155,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1155},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcxxXLD4cPnzGVPhzZK7Q","attributionMcpServer":"canvas","attributionMcpTool":"canvas_render","type":"assistant","uuid":"86237a7c-111b-42f9-81e2-31f7cd3ab8a1","timestamp":"2026-07-12T22:32:54.135Z","userType":"external","ent